4 § 110. FISCALYEAR
The fiscal year of the City and the City School District shall begin on the
first day of July and end on the last day of June and end on the last day of June
of each calendar year. The fiscal year shall constitute the budget and
accounting year as used in this charter.
5 § 111. BONDING OF CITY OFFICIALS
6 The Mayor, councilors, members of the Police Department, City Manager,
7 Finance Director, Superintendent of Public Works, TaxCollector, and Clerk,
8 and Treasurer shall annually be bonded by the City for the faithful discharge of
9 their respective duties, as provided by State statute, and the expense of said
10 bonds to be paid by the City.
